flowchart TD
    A[request] --> B{L1 base exists?}
    B -- ready --> H[serve - cache hit]
    B -- failed or stale --> R[reclaim + regenerate]
    B -- missing --> I{guarded insert wins?}
    I -- yes --> G[generate + mark ready]
    I -- no --> P[poll until ready or failed]
    P --> H
    G --> H
    R --> H
